text: Montillières-sur-Orne is a commune. It is found in the region Normandy in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2019 and consists of the former communes of Trois-Monts (the seat) and Goupillières.Arrêté préfectoral 28 September 2018, p. 91 == References == Category:2019 establishments in France Category:Communes in Calvados
title: Montillières-sur-Orne
